 Description: Binary utilities for db42
 Files: bin
 DocFiles: LICENSE
<<
SplitOff3: <<
 Package: %N-doc
 Description: Documentation for db42
 Files: share/doc/db42-doc
 DocFiles: LICENSE
<<
